Interface ISingleQueryModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IQueryModel
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBaseBuildDefinitionQueryModel.IBuildDefinitionQueryModel, IBaseBuildEngineQueryModel.IBuildEngineQueryModel, IBaseBuildFolderEntryQueryModel.IBuildFolderEntryQueryModel, IBaseBuildResultQueryModel.IBuildResultQueryModel, IBaseCoreDescriptorQueryModel.ICoreDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseDataSetQueryModel.IDataSetQueryModel, IBaseFolderDescriptorQueryModel.IFolderDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseReportDescriptorQueryModel.IReportDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseReportQueryDescriptorQueryModel.IReportQueryDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseSharableDescriptorQueryModel.ISharableDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseStorageNodeQueryModel.IStorageNodeQueryModel, IDynamicItemQueryModel, IDynamicQueryModel, ISingleItemQueryModel

    public interface ISingleQueryModel
extends IQueryModel
    Defines the query model for query model roots, or single valued references to Items or Helpers. Instances can be acquired by using the root associated with an item. For example, if an Item subclasses was named Child then the root of the query model could be acquired using ChildQueryModel.ROOT.
    Since:
    0.5
